---
---
<section id="solutions" class="layout bound-x scheme-default py-[32px] m-0 border-0 relative">
  <div class="layout-section-y relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-screen-vp10 mx-auto text-center mb-12" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
      <span class="text-timefold-accent uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold text-sm">Solutions</span>
      <h2 class="tracking-tight text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-3 mb-4">
        Your shortcut to world-class optimization
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-slate-400 text-lg">
        Optimization deep tech, under the hood of your systems. Get started in minutes, scale to millions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid justify-center gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <article class="bg-timefold-card border border-timefold-border p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-timefold-primary hover:shadow-glow-primary hover:-translate-y-1 group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-timefold-primary/20 text-timefold-primary flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-timefold-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-xl">We handle complexity</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Scheduling at scale is notoriously complex. We standardized out-of-the-box solutions for the world's most complex problems.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-timefold-card border border-timefold-border p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-timefold-primary hover:shadow-glow-primary hover:-translate-y-1 group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-timefold-primary/20 text-timefold-primary flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-timefold-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-xl">Start where others finish</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Embed Timefold and skip years of risky in-house development. Go from POC to production in less than 3 months.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-timefold-card border border-timefold-border p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-timefold-primary hover:shadow-glow-primary hover:-translate-y-1 group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-timefold-primary/20 text-timefold-primary flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-timefold-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 8V4m0 0h4M4 4l5 5m11-1V4m0 0h-4m4 0l-5 5M4 16v4m0 0h4m-4 0l5-5m11 5l-5-5m5 5v-4m0 4h-4" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-xl">Built for your reality</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Our APIs cover 95% of required complexity and are easily extensible whenever new business rules are needed.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-timefold-card border border-timefold-border p-8 rounded-2xl flex flex-col gap-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-timefold-primary hover:shadow-glow-primary hover:-translate-y-1 group" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-timefold-primary/20 text-timefold-primary flex items-center justify-center group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:bg-timefold-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
          <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122" /></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-xl">One-click optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your UX, our AI. Keep your interface and workflows. Go live with minimal change and gain intelligent scheduling.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
